<br>
Currently if you are moving, turning, or attacking on a horse you will not meditate. If you are standing still you will meditate. If you are casting, depending when you cast the server will not give you a med pulse tat tic, but if its a long casting spell and you pass another tic while casting it will consider you medding.<br>
<br>
This is great for casters in outdoor zones. They dont have to worry about sit agro, dont have to worry about forgetting to sit down, and can sometimes gain mana when casting(depending when the spell is cast, and the duration of the spell).<br>
<br>
Whenever im rebuffing with right clicks i first pop out my horse, gives me an little extra mana. I dont fight on it, since it does nothing but hinder combat.<br>
<br>
<br>
There are many aa routes you can choose, its really up to you. The horse is kinda nice, but its utility, unless you spend a lot of time right clicking and not fighting its not gonna help you kill any faster. It does cut down travel, and is nice for corpse runs.<br>
<br>
Slay undead is a nice skill, but you need to stick with it. Level one will be disappointing, it wont really pay off till level 3. So you are looking at an 18 point investment.....once you get slay undead however it will help you get points faster in undead areas. You already sunk 12 into combat fury, so you might wanna just continue along this path.<br>
<br>
There are also some nice arches such as combat agility, and spell casting reinforcement. Both are very nice skills.<br>
<br>
Healing adept while not so good for solo, is really nice if you use prexus a lot. But unless you raid a lot i wouldnt recommend this one yet.<br>
<br>
2h bash is alrso a decent skill, never have to be without bash again. And adds a few dps to boot.<br>
<br>
Anyway lots of options, and its up to you. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showPrevMessage?topicID=1063.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showNextMessage?topicID=1063.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1063.topic&index=1><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=1063.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.threadControl?topicID=1063.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1063.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1063.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="paladinsofnorrathgeneral">General<option value="paladinsofnorrathfrm13">Crusader's Warhall<option value="paladinsofnorrathfrm16">Arena of the Holy<option value="paladinsofnorrathgodsmightroleplaytavern">God's Might